         <em>Family Back to School Night</em>
         <br> See the fun projects we've been working on and your child's works of art at Family Back to School Night. 
         <br> 
         <br> 
         <strong>December 24, 2014</strong> 
         <em>Infant, Toddler and Preschool Winter Break</em>
         <br> Enjoy your holiday as we break for the winter. The center will be closed on December 24, 2014 and reopen January 2, 2015. 
         <br> 
         <br> 
         <strong>May 4-8, 2015</strong> 
         <em>Teacher Appreciation Week</em>
         <br> Let's celebrate our fabulous teachers who spend their days helping every child achieve success. 
         <a href="http://www.pta.org/parents/content.cfm?ItemNumber=3270" target="_blank">Find out ways to show your appreciation.</a>
        </div> 
